facebrick (0.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Cap input of status updates to the maximum size of a Facebook update
    (@roamer145)
  * Some minor UI changes, including slightly more visually appealing colours.
  * Fix newlines in text appearing as a box character instead of ..a newline.
  * Make dates take up less text to allow for more room for names.

 -- Robin Burchell <viroteck@viroteck.net>  Fri, 28 May 2010 22:38:02 +0100

facebrick (0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * UI changes to newsfeed: newest posts are now at the top, as is entry.
  * Maemo progress indicator and information box when liking/disliking a post.
  * Improvements to avatar loading: doesn't try to load all simultaneously.
  * [EXPERIMENTAL]: Application/sharing posts support (photos/etc)

 -- Robin Burchell <viroteck@viroteck.net>  Sat, 17 Apr 2010 18:28:12 +0000

facebrick (0.2.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * The original post is now shown when viewing comments (thanks to jaysire @ tmo and others)
  * Downscale avatars greater than 50px - Facebook occasionally give us these for some reason
  * Correctly display newlines in status/comments (thanks to zombiepig @ tmo)
  * Change 'Dislike' text to 'Unlike'

 -- Robin Burchell <viroteck@viroteck.net>  Mon, 12 Apr 2010 20:58:22 +0000

facebrick (0.2.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Use a progress indicator while loading comments on a newspost
  * Add a menu item to synchronise comments on a newspost
